She saw another bot come in and start firing on her. she fires at both bots. 
  "HEY Stringtra, We got more company.  We could use some backup if you have 
any."  She kept firing on both bots.  All of a sudden, she heard the click, 
click as her gun went out of ammo.
"Blast!" She put the gun away and ran to Stringtra and Quickstrike.  She 
grabbed the other side of Quickstrike.
"RUN FOR IT OR WE ARE GOING TO BE SLAGGED!"
